00:30:17,500 --> 00:30:18,500
Do you want

572
00:30:18,620 --> 00:30:20,220
to watch an opera with
a focus on singing and acting

573
00:30:20,620 --> 00:30:21,940
or an opera with a focus on combat moves?

574
00:30:22,100 --> 00:30:23,700
He is the Marquis' younger brother

575
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:26,460
Xu Lingkuan of the Xu Family.

576
00:30:28,460 --> 00:30:29,340
How about I

577
00:30:29,460 --> 00:30:30,940
recite the opera titles for you?

578
00:30:31,060 --> 00:30:33,820
Lingkuan, stop clowning around.

579
00:30:33,940 --> 00:30:34,780
You might scare

580
00:30:34,860 --> 00:30:36,500
the young ladies.

581
00:30:48,020 --> 00:30:49,380
(Danyang)
