582
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:50,300
Come on.

583
00:30:50,380 --> 00:30:53,020
Hold Lingkuan in check.

584
00:30:53,300 --> 00:30:54,020
Mom.

585
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:55,860
Lingkuan was only being kind.

586
00:30:55,940 --> 00:30:57,300
So many elders

587
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:58,540
and young ladies are here.

588
00:30:58,700 --> 00:31:00,020
We can't let the opera actors

589
00:31:00,100 --> 00:31:01,460
come in and present the list of operas.

590
00:31:02,500 --> 00:31:03,460
Alright.

591
00:31:03,660 --> 00:31:05,740
Greet the Madams.

592
00:31:16,180 --> 00:31:17,940
Let's watch an opera with
a focus on singing and acting.

593
00:31:18,620 --> 00:31:19,660
The operas with a focus on combat moves

594
00:31:19,740 --> 00:31:21,620
are all about fighting

595
00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:23,700
and actors doing somersaults.

596
00:31:23,740 --> 00:31:24,900
You watch them till the end,

597
00:31:24,980 --> 00:31:25,900
but you don't understand

598
00:31:25,980 --> 00:31:27,900
what's going on.

599
00:31:29,980 --> 00:31:32,020
Then we'll watch "The Peony Pavilion".

600
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:33,140
I like that.

601
00:31:33,220 --> 00:31:33,820
Alright.

602
00:31:34,020 --> 00:31:35,220
I'll make preparations.

603
00:31:35,300 --> 00:31:35,900
Yes.

604
00:31:36,020 --> 00:31:37,820
Great Madam, His Lordship is here.

605
00:31:47,180 --> 00:31:48,420
Young ladies,

606
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:49,300
please come with me

607
00:31:49,380 --> 00:31:50,620
and hide behind the folding screen.

608
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:54,660
His Lordship is here.

609
00:31:54,860 --> 00:31:56,100
Why aren't you moving?

610
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:56,620
Come and change

611
00:31:56,700 --> 00:31:57,300
out of your costume.

612
00:31:57,380 --> 00:31:57,980
Yes.

613
00:32:03,540 --> 00:32:04,780
I pay my respects to you, Mother.

614
00:32:05,980 --> 00:32:07,820
Greetings the Madams.

615
00:32:09,740 --> 00:32:10,700
Greetings, mother-in-law.

616
00:32:11,820 --> 00:32:13,140
We're family.

617
00:32:13,540 --> 00:32:15,020
You don't have to be formal.

618
00:32:15,420 --> 00:32:16,700
I hope you'll forgive me

619
00:32:16,900 --> 00:32:18,140
if you ever find
the reception unsatisfactory.

620
00:32:18,860 --> 00:32:21,860
You're too kind, Marquis.

621
00:32:22,220 --> 00:32:22,820
I won't disturb you

622
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:24,140
any longer.

623
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:44,340
(Success)

624
00:32:45,900 --> 00:32:54,460
♪My heart♪

625
00:32:54,460 --> 00:32:56,140
(Depends)

626
00:32:57,260 --> 00:33:06,660
♪Happens to flip♪

627
00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:11,140
♪As I stand by a plum tree♪

628
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:12,180
Great Madam.

629
00:33:17,300 --> 00:33:19,980
Greetings, Madams and ladies.

630
00:33:21,060 --> 00:33:22,700
♪These plants♪
Her Ladyship said

631
00:33:22,860 --> 00:33:24,260
♪Stir up♪
her health condition didn't allow her

632
00:33:24,340 --> 00:33:26,500
to keep you company.

633
00:33:26,580 --> 00:33:28,340
She felt sorry.

634
00:33:28,500 --> 00:33:30,540
So she had people prepare kites.

635
00:33:30,740 --> 00:33:33,140
When you've grown tired of the opera,

636
00:33:33,300 --> 00:33:35,020
you may fly the kites together.

637
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:37,060
Great Madam.

638
00:33:37,140 --> 00:33:38,220
♪Sentiments in me♪
I don't want to watch the opera.

639
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:39,460
I want to fly the kites.

640
00:33:39,860 --> 00:33:41,060
Me too.

641
00:33:42,380 --> 00:33:43,940
Alright.

642
00:33:44,060 --> 00:33:45,220
You can go.

643
00:33:48,940 --> 00:33:49,940
Lady Qiao.

644
00:33:51,740 --> 00:33:53,140
You know the Xu Family's mansion

645
00:33:53,260 --> 00:33:54,060
more than any

646
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:55,820
other young ladies.

647
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:56,940
Therefore,

648
00:33:57,060 --> 00:33:57,900
Her Ladyship

649
00:33:58,020 --> 00:33:59,380
hopes that you

650
00:33:59,500 --> 00:34:01,260
will show the other young ladies

651
00:34:01,380 --> 00:34:02,300
around.

652
00:34:03,340 --> 00:34:04,660
I want to stay...

653
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:09,220
♪Their life and death
are for others to decide♪

654
00:34:09,220 --> 00:34:10,620
But Madam Xu made a request

655
00:34:10,740 --> 00:34:12,580
and I won't turn her down.

656
00:34:12,580 --> 00:34:14,580
♪And I have nowhere
to vent my sorrows♪

657
00:34:14,620 --> 00:34:16,500
Ladies who want to fly the kites,

658
00:34:16,620 --> 00:34:17,420
come with me.

659
00:34:19,060 --> 00:34:20,020
Erniang.

660
00:34:20,820 --> 00:34:23,620
Don't you like this opera?

661
00:34:24,460 --> 00:34:25,700
Stay till it ends.

662
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:27,220
I can

663
00:34:27,380 --> 00:34:28,820
watch this opera another day.

664
00:34:29,140 --> 00:34:30,460
But I shouldn't

665
00:34:30,580 --> 00:34:31,820
waste my eldest sister's kindness.

666
00:34:31,820 --> 00:34:44,860
♪I will wait on this rainy day♪

667
00:34:46,180 --> 00:34:47,100
Shiyi.

668
00:34:47,100 --> 00:34:55,660
♪For the right man to show up♪

669
00:34:55,700 --> 00:34:56,620
Mother.

670
00:34:57,420 --> 00:34:58,740
Go with Nanny Tao

671
00:34:58,900 --> 00:35:00,340
and meet your eldest sister.

672
00:35:00,340 --> 00:35:03,180
♪Even if it means my death.♪

673
00:35:03,220 --> 00:35:04,460
Yes, Mother.

674
00:35:07,140 --> 00:35:09,340
(On)

675
00:35:12,700 --> 00:35:16,460
(Effort)
(Success depends on effort)

676
00:35:29,020 --> 00:35:29,620
Your Ladyship.

677
00:35:33,060 --> 00:35:34,180
It seems

678
00:35:35,620 --> 00:35:37,380
water has mixed with ink.

679
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:41,460
Your Ladyship, it's all set.

680
00:35:43,020 --> 00:35:44,420
Let her in.

681
00:35:44,860 --> 00:35:47,500
Your Ladyship, it's Lady Shiyi.

682
00:35:49,460 --> 00:35:51,980
Lady Erniang went with Qiao Lianfang.

683
00:35:58,660 --> 00:36:00,500
It must be fate's work.

684
00:36:06,180 --> 00:36:08,020
(I finally got rid of them.)

685
00:36:24,060 --> 00:36:25,340
What is wrong with you?

686
00:36:25,420 --> 00:36:26,420
I'm sorry, Lady Qiao.

687
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:27,620
I was in a hurry.

688
00:36:27,740 --> 00:36:28,980
Let me wipe it clean.

689
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:30,660
No need.

690
00:36:30,780 --> 00:36:32,140
Get up.

691
00:36:32,420 --> 00:36:33,540
Thank you, Lady Qiao.

692
00:36:36,940 --> 00:36:37,700
Lady Qiao,

693
00:36:37,780 --> 00:36:39,180
come to the courtyard with me

694
00:36:39,260 --> 00:36:40,380
if you don't mind.

695
00:36:40,460 --> 00:36:41,060
You can get your clothes cleaned

696
00:36:41,180 --> 00:36:42,220
as soon as possible there.

697
00:36:42,620 --> 00:36:43,620
The courtyard?

698
00:36:44,420 --> 00:36:47,100
(Maybe I'll run into
the Marquis in the courtyard.)

699
00:36:48,300 --> 00:36:50,260
I guess I have no choice.

700
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:51,980
Lady Qiao, this way.

701
00:36:59,620 --> 00:37:00,580
Lady Qiao, this way.

702
00:37:01,820 --> 00:37:02,820
(Jing'an Pavilion)

703
00:37:02,820 --> 00:37:04,300
This is the place, Lady Qiao.

704
00:37:16,100 --> 00:37:17,700
I stayed indoors for too long.

705
00:37:18,420 --> 00:37:20,140
So I wanted to come out for a walk.

706
00:37:21,420 --> 00:37:23,340
I hope you don't mind, Shiyi.

707
00:37:34,060 --> 00:37:35,060
Lady Qiao.

708
00:37:35,940 --> 00:37:36,820
Wait here for a while, please.

709
00:37:36,900 --> 00:37:37,740
Let me bring you

710
00:37:37,820 --> 00:37:38,740
some clean clothes,

711
00:37:38,820 --> 00:37:39,900
so you won't catch a cold.

712
00:37:41,820 --> 00:37:43,060
But...

713
00:37:44,060 --> 00:37:45,060
Don't worry.

714
00:37:45,180 --> 00:37:46,740
Nobody will come here.

715
00:37:48,140 --> 00:37:49,100
Alright.

716
00:38:00,060 --> 00:38:01,140
Shiyi.

717
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:05,340
Where do you live at the family house?

718
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:06,820
Yuanniang,

719
00:38:06,900 --> 00:38:08,020
I live in Lvyun Suite.

720
00:38:08,780 --> 00:38:10,900
I remember that it has a warm room.

721
00:38:11,420 --> 00:38:12,660
The warm room

722
00:38:13,060 --> 00:38:14,300
is bright and cozy.

723
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:16,620
I often read in the warm room

724
00:38:16,740 --> 00:38:18,820
when I was a kid.

725
00:38:32,580 --> 00:38:34,580
Are you tired?

726
00:38:34,700 --> 00:38:35,620
How about we

727
00:38:35,700 --> 00:38:37,140
find a place to rest?

728
00:38:41,380 --> 00:38:43,580
Jing'an Pavilion is just
a stone's throw away.

729
00:38:44,100 --> 00:38:45,940
Let's rest there.

730
00:38:46,900 --> 00:38:47,580
Alright.

731
00:38:47,740 --> 00:38:48,820
This way.

732
00:39:26,140 --> 00:39:33,020
(Jing'an Pavilion)

733
00:39:50,020 --> 00:39:50,860
My Lord!

734
00:39:50,860 --> 00:39:52,860
(Jing'an Pavilion)

735
00:40:11,490 --> 00:40:14,340
♪In the cold darkness of midnight,
a sigh is heard♪

736
00:40:14,940 --> 00:40:17,740
♪Who picked up the paintbrush
to draw loneliness♪

737
00:40:19,060 --> 00:40:25,620
♪In my life, I can draw everything,
but lovesickness♪

738
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:28,100
♪The mountain city is waiting for rain♪

739
00:40:29,100 --> 00:40:32,700
♪I am waiting for you
to pass in my memory♪

740
00:40:33,140 --> 00:40:39,300
♪The sky is in a more lonely color
than your face♪

741
00:40:39,740 --> 00:40:42,260
♪The wind rises
and the candle light flickers♪

742
00:40:43,060 --> 00:40:45,740
♪The thin clothes
can't stand the cold days♪

743
00:40:46,940 --> 00:40:53,780
♪Full of twists and turns,
fate is untold♪

744
00:40:54,180 --> 00:40:56,380
♪I ground my thoughts into ink♪

745
00:40:57,380 --> 00:41:00,820
♪But I still can't sketch your contours♪

746
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:07,100
♪How could the ink
and paper exhaust our stories♪

747
00:41:07,940 --> 00:41:14,820
♪Who picked up the pen
to disturb the heart♪

748
00:41:14,920 --> 00:41:21,820
♪Who visited to remind me of the past♪

749
00:41:22,100 --> 00:41:25,540
♪If feelings can be kept in mind,
but cannot be confessed♪

750
00:41:26,820 --> 00:41:29,120
♪I won't escape from whatever end♪

751
00:41:30,420 --> 00:41:36,140
♪In the dim lantern light,
with you there is me♪

752
00:41:36,140 --> 00:41:43,060
♪Who picked up the pen
to set free lonely tears♪

753
00:41:43,300 --> 00:41:49,820
♪Whoever visited my life,
only you stayed all the days♪

754
00:41:50,380 --> 00:41:53,900
♪If the moth doesn't fly into the fire♪

755
00:41:54,980 --> 00:41:57,940
♪How can it be said to be persistent♪

756
00:41:58,420 --> 00:42:06,060
♪Coming to the end of your story,
there is me♪
